<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Innocency" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Innocency,</orth> 1) freedom from a particular guilt: <bibl n="shak. jn 4.3.110" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 3, 110</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.84" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 84</bibl> (O. Edd. <emph>innocence</emph>). <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.2.39" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 2, 39</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.5.20" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 5, 20</bibl> (Q<hi rend="sub">1</hi> <emph>innocence</emph>).<lb />2) freedom from any thought of evil: <bibl n="shak. mm 3.2.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 2, 10</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.186" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 186</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.3.63" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 63</bibl>.
